and the devils are here.

62
00:06:18,011 --> 00:06:20,912
I pray to god
and our holy mother
that they will not get in.

63
00:06:20,914 --> 00:06:23,382
But if, god forbid,
they were to do so,

64
00:06:23,384 --> 00:06:25,417
Make sure they do not
capture you alive.

65
00:06:25,419 --> 00:06:27,052
-(all whispering)
-(bells tolling)

66
